United States\n\t\t\t Code", "@value": "usc/31/3123"}], "#text": "In the event that the\n\t\t\t debt of the United States Government, as defined in ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(a)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t general"}, "#text": "\n        ", "@id": "H7E74DFDAD5424AC3AE5CB91127005842"}, {"#tail": "\n    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": ", is amended by redesignating ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "Section 324 of title 31, United States\n\t\t\t Code", "@value": "usc/31/324"}, {"#tail": " as ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "subsection (c)", "@value": "usc/31/324/c"}, {"#tail": ", and by\n\t\t\t inserting after ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "subsection (e)", "@value": "usc/31/324/e"}, {"#tail": " the following:", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "subsection (b)", "@value": "usc/31/324/b"}], "#text": "\n          "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(b)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "Special rule for\n\t\t\t insufficiency of funds"}, "quoted-block": {"@style": "USC", "after-quoted-block": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "."}, "#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "subsection": [{"#tail": "\n          ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " expects that there will be\n\t\t\t\tinsufficient funds available to dispose of all obligations consisting of\n\t\t\t\tinterest and principal of the debt held by the public on the next calendar day\n\t\t\t\ton which such obligations are due, then the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Secretary", "@entity-id": "2000"}, {"#tail": " shall extend the\n\t\t\t\tmaturities of any other obligations under ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Secretary", "@entity-id": "2000"}, {"#tail": " and refuse to issue\n\t\t\t\twarrants under ", "@entity-type": "uscode", "#text": "section (a)", "@va